{"data":[{"date":"14:27 14/07","title":"T\u00e2y Ban Nha d\u1ecda b\u1eaft Ronaldo t\u1ea1i Italia","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/tay-ban-nha-doa-bat-ronaldo-tai-italia.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"4221","checkdouble":"191161"},{"date":"14:30 14/07","title":"\"Th\u00e1nh \u0103n v\u1ea1\" Neymar hot nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean Facebook t\u1ea1i Anh m\u00f9a World Cup 2018","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/14/thanh-an-va-neymar-hot-nhat-tren-facebook-tai-anh-mua-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e1c fan x\u1ee9 s\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00f9 nh\u1eafc t\u00ean Neymar, Messi, C. Ronaldo nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Tam s\u01b0 nh\u01b0 Harry Kane, Lingard...</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Theo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea c\u1ee7a Facebook, trong m\u00f9a World Cup 2018, th\u00e1nh \u0103n v\u1ea1 Neymar l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng t\u1ea1i Anh nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t. Ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a PSG c\u00f3 hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, g\u00f3p c\u00f4ng gi\u00fap tuy\u1ec3n Brazil v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ebfn ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0y \"g\u00e2y b\u00e3o\" m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n \u0103n v\u1ea1 trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u00e1nh \u0103n v\u1ea1 Neymar hot nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean Facebook t\u1ea1i Anh m\u00f9a World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u00e1nh \u0103n v\u1ea1 Neymar hot nh\u1ea5t tr\u00ean Facebook t\u1ea1i Anh m\u00f9a World Cup h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/ney-6889-1531537635.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Neymar \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng Facebook \u1edf Anh nh\u1eafc t\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 Messi, C. Ronaldo v\u00e0 Harry Kane.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ee9ng sau Neymar l\u00e0 Messi. Si\u00eau sao c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Argentina kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng khi \"t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i\" trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng g\u1eb7p Ireland v\u00e0 Croatia. Sau \u0111\u00f3 anh k\u1ecbp to\u1ea3 s\u00e1ng trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng Argentina v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng x\u1ee9 tango v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i s\u1edbm d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 3-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nX\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 ba trong danh s\u00e1ch l\u00e0 C. Ronaldo. Tr\u00e1i v\u1edbi Messi, C. Ronaldo to\u1ea3 s\u00e1ng r\u1ef1c r\u1ee1 khi ghi t\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng g\u1eb7p T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 Mar\u1ed1c. Tuy nhi\u00ean, si\u00eau sao c\u1ee7a Real l\u1ea1i \"t\u1ecbt ng\u00f2i\" trong c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn sau. B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u0169ng b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng knock-out sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi 6 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Harry Kane l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quan t\u00e2m nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u1ee9ng th\u1ee9 t\u01b0 trong danh s\u00e1ch. Ba v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ebfp theo \u0111\u1ec1u\u00a0 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Anh g\u1ed3m Harry Maguire, Jesse Lingard v\u00e0 Jordan Henderson. Trong top 10 c\u00f2n c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec7n di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Ramos, De Gea v\u00e0 Rashford.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n12 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng Facebook \u1edf Anh nh\u1eafc t\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t m\u00f9a World Cup 2018<br>\r\n<br>\r\n1. Neymar<br>\r\n2. Lionel Messi<br>\r\n3. Cristiano Ronaldo<br>\r\n4. Harry Kane<br>\r\n5. Harry Maguire<br>\r\n6. Jesse Lingard<br>\r\n7. Jordan Henderson<br>\r\n8. Sergio Ramos<br>\r\n9. Marcus Rashford<br>\r\n10. David De Gea<br>\r\n11. Luis Suarez<br>\r\n12. Luka Modric</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4220","checkdouble":"191162"},{"date":"14:00 14/07","title":"TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP H\u1ea3i Ph\u00f2ng 1-0 B\u00ecnh D\u01b0\u01a1ng (H1): Si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/hai-phong-vs-binh-duong-vong-19-vleague-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold;