in:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp HAGL vs C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u HAGL Ho\u00e0ng Anh Gia Lai vs C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 v\u00f2ng 19 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00fac 17h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 14/7.</h2><h2>Tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp HAGL vs C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1: C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt li\u00ean t\u1ee5c di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u1eddng thu\u1eadt t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u HAGL Ho\u00e0ng Anh Gia Lai vs C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 v\u00f2ng 19 gi\u1ea3i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch qu\u1ed1c gia V\u0110QG Vi\u1ec7t Nam l\u00fac 17h00 chi\u1ec1u ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay 14/7.</h2>\r\nKh\u00f4ng xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, vui l\u00f2ng click t\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e2y <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/hagl-vs-can-tho-vong-19-vleague-2018-372-191160.html\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 0, 0);\"><u><strong>TR\u1ef0C TI\u1ebeP HAGL VS C\u1ea6N TH\u01a0</strong></u></span></span><br>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4218","checkdouble":"191160"},{"date":"15:42 14/07","title":"Ronaldo v\u00e0 Benzema s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u nhau \u1edf Serie A?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/27/ronaldo-va-benzema-sap-doi-dau-nhau-o-serie-a.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Karim Benzema c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, HLV Carlo Ancelotti \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u1edf s\u00e2n San Paolo.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Benzema</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Carlo Ancelotti \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m thay th\u1ebf Sarri d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Napoli t\u1eeb m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u0103ng c\u01b0\u1eddng l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n San Paolo m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd h\u01a1n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Karim Benzema c\u1ee7a Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Karim Benzema c\u1ee7a Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/27/Napoli-muon-mua-Karim-Benzema-cua-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Benzema</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nAncelotti \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia mua th\u00eam ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o. Napoli mu\u1ed1n mua Karim Benzema c\u1ee7a Real Madrid, HLV Carlo Ancelotti \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u0169 \u1edf s\u00e2n San Paolo.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Benzema lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng ghi qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng anh l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0o l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Ancelotti \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Benzema v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n Napoli chi \u0111\u1eadm \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987. Theo La Sexta, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/chinh-thuc-real-xac-nhan-ronaldo-cap-ben-juventus-180-190888.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus</span>, n\u1ebfu Benzema c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Napoli, hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed1i tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi nhau \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 Napoli c\u00f3 Benzema</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef Ronaldo \u1edf l\u1ea1i, vi\u1ec7c ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 mu\u1ed1n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Perez b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c gi\u1eef anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Benzema mo ty so sau sai sot cua Karius\" title=\"Benzema m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 sau sai s\u00f3t c\u1ee7a Karius\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/27/ronaldo-va-benzema-sap-doi-dau-nhau-o-serie-a.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 nh\u1ea3 Benzema cho Napoli</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong nh\u1eefng m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, Ronaldo l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng m\u00eanh m\u00f4ng tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a Los Blancos, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ea5t th\u00eam nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd \u01b0u ti\u00ean gi\u1eef Benzema, Isco, Bale hay Asensio. M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 Napoli ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi t\u1edbi 35 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng song kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng h\u1ecd chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng ng\u00f4i sao 31 tu\u1ed5i \u0111ang r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y t\u00e2n HLV Lopetegui c\u1ee7a Real kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u00e1n Benzema v\u1edbi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 gi\u00e1 n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4217","checkdouble":"191165"},{"date":"17:04 14/07","title":"Roma b\u00e1o tin vui cho Real v\u1ee5 th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/4/24/roma-bao-tin-vui-cho-real-vu-thu-mon-alisson.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Roma b\u00e1n Alisson n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng quan t\u00e2m Alisson</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Alisson l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t Serie A. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n. Trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Brazil c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn s\u1ed1 1 trong khung g\u1ed7.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Roma b\u00e1n Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Roma b\u00e1n Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/11/Roma-ban-Alisson-voi-gia-50-trieu-bang-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn h\u1ecfi mua Alisson\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil gi\u00fap anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng theo \u0111u\u1ed5i. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-dat-duoc-thoa-thuan-mua-thu-mon-moi-voi-gia-sieu-khung-180-182517.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Alisson</span>, h\u1ecd nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho Navas, ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eafp b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 32.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m Alisson, h\u1ecd mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Braizl th\u1ebf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Karuis, ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean m\u1eafc nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChelsea c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Roma. Vi\u1ec7c Thibaut Courtois t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 mu\u1ed1n ra \u0111i l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London ph\u1ea3i l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Roma s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng b\u00e1n Alisson</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Roma b\u00e1n Alisson n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Italia \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson\" title=\"Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/4/24/roma-bao-tin-vui-cho-real-vu-thu-mon-alisson.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Roma h\u1ea1 gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Alisson</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGianLuca Di Marzio.com kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Roma ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn h\u1ea1 gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992, theo \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o ch\u1ecbu chi ra 45 \u0111\u1ebfn 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 h\u1ecd \u0111\u00f2i \u0111\u1ee7 70 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Alisson.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 l\u1edbn, nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh t\u00e0i n\u0103ng nh\u01b0 Alisson nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd khi\u1ebfn Chelsea, Liverpool ho\u1eb7c Real ph\u1ea3i \u201cph\u00e1 k\u00e9t\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eeba tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 t\u1eeb World Cup 2018, Brazil c\u1ee7a Alisson \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay khi d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1ec1 ph\u00eda c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1992 anh v\u1eabn kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac \u1edf Roma v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 Italia c\u00f3 to\u00e0n quy\u1ec1n quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4216","checkdouble":"191170"},{"date":"16:02 14/07","title":"Ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay, Gareth Bale x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/14/ngay-hom-nay-gareth-bale-xac-dinh-tuong-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u00e1o ch\u00ed T\u00e2y Ban Nha cho bi\u1ebft, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Gareth Bale x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai v\u00e0o h\u00f4m nay, sau cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 v\u1edbi HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Julen Lopetegui.\r\n</h2><h2>Bale s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 1 trong 2 ng\u00f4i sao tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai (c\u00f9ng Cris Ronaldo) ngay sau tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft C1, Gareth Bale \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng r\u1eddi Real Madrid. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 no n\u00ea danh hi\u1ec7u t\u1ea1i T\u00e2y Ban Nha v\u00e0 ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ti\u1ebfp. Quan tr\u1ecdng h\u01a1n, anh \u0111\u00e3 ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, v\u00e0 \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm s\u1ef1 gi\u1ea3i tho\u00e1t cho s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay Los Blancos \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Juve, theo \u0111u\u1ed5i cu\u1ed9c phi\u00eau l\u01b0u m\u1edbi. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn t\u1edbi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Gareth Bale, r\u1eb1ng anh s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u1ebfm l\u1ea5y v\u1ecb tr\u00ed cao nh\u1ea5t, hay ra \u0111i theo ni\u1ec1m c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ng\u00f4i sao x\u1ee9 Wales cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng t\u1ea1i Real, nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i chia s\u1ebb t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh, trong khi t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gareth Bale x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai sau khi c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi HLV Lopetegui\" title=\"Gareth Bale x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/ngay-hom-nay-gareth-bale-xac-dinh-tuong-lai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gareth Bale x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai sau khi c\u00f3 cu\u1ed9c trao \u0111\u1ed5i v\u1edbi HLV Lopetegui</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m trong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng mong \u0111\u1ee3i v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i sau m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i, c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u1eaft \u0111\u1ee9t li\u00ean l\u1ea1c. Th\u00fa th\u1ef1c, t\u00f4i th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng xem l\u1ea1i b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i s\u1ebd th\u1ea3o lu\u1eadn v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 t\u00ecm ra h\u01b0\u1edbng gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t&rdquo; &ndash; Gareth Bale chia s\u1ebb.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo \u0111\u00f3, HLV Lopetegui l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi r\u1ea5t ch\u00fa tr\u1ecdng ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n t\u00e0i n\u0103ng b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 T\u00e2y Ban Nha. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, \u00f4ng s\u1ebd tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Isco v\u00e0 trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n cho Lucas Vazquez, hay Marco Asensio. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn t\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Gareth Bale x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p ra \u0111i, Premier League v\u00e0 Man United ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 b\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 x\u1ee9 Wales. Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 100 tri\u1ec7u euro \u0111\u1ec3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Bale, v\u00e0 v\u1eabn \u0111ang ch\u1edd m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-bi-ung-ho-hazard-gia-nhap-real-madrid-voi-gia-ky-luc-180-191140.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/11/hlv-bi-ung-ho-hazard-gia-nhap-real-madrid-voi-gia-ky-luc.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/hlv-bi-ung-ho-hazard-gia-nhap-real-madrid-voi-gia-ky-luc-180-191140.html\">HLV B\u1ec9 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Hazard gia nh\u1eadp Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a HLV Roberto Martinez xoay quanh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao Chelsea tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn B\u1ec9 vs Anh tranh h\u1ea1ng ba World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-chinh-thuc-ra-thong-bao-ve-thuong-vu-neymar-180-191138.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/real-madrid-chinh-thuc-ra-thong-bao-ve-thuong-vu-neymar.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-chinh-thuc-ra-thong-bao-ve-thuong-vu-neymar-180-191138.html\">Real Madrid ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u1ec1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Neymar</span><br>\r\nTrang ch\u1ee7 CLB ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u0103ng b\u00e0i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao Neymar t\u1eeb Paris Saint-Germain.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4215","checkdouble":"191171"},{"date":"14:20 14/07","title":"T\u00e2n HLV Arsenal s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng gi\u00fap Ozil t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/7/hlv-emery-phat-bieu-ve-ozil.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ozil. T\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Arsenal tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng gi\u00fap ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c t\u00ecm l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ozil ch\u00ecm trong ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 k\u1ebft th\u00fac kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng h\u01a1n v\u1edbi Mesut Ozil. Nh\u1eefng l\u00f9m x\u00f9m xung quanh c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng s\u1eafp h\u1ebft h\u1ea1n khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eadp trung thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Ozil tr\u1edf n\u00ean h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c t\u1ea7m th\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 \u0111i k\u00e8m v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y l\u1ea1c quan c\u1ee7a Arsenal.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay c\u1ea3 khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00e0nh t\u1eb7ng m\u1ed9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c, nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a Ozil v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n. C\u00f2n Arsenal, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch Premier League \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 6 tr\u00ean BXH Premier League v\u00e0 n\u0103m th\u1ee9 2 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ozil v\u00e0 h\u1ee9a gi\u00fap anh h\u1ed3i sinh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ozil v\u00e0 h\u1ee9a gi\u00fap anh h\u1ed3i sinh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/28/HLV-Emery-phat-bieu-ve-Ozil-va-hua-giup-anh-hoi-sinh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Ozil b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch c\u1ea3 t\u1ea1i Arsenal l\u1eabn \u0110T\u00a0\u0110\u1ee9c</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ed1n \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb C\u0110V Arsenal ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edbt v\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n, khi l\u00ean \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c, Ozil c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 b\u00ecnh y\u00ean. Cu\u1ed9c g\u1eb7p m\u1eb7t nh\u00e2n v\u1eadt g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i: T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 Recep Tayyip Erdogan r\u1ed3i t\u1eb7ng \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u khi\u1ebfn cho ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y nh\u1eadn v\u1ec1 nh\u1eefng ti\u1ebfng la \u00f3, hu\u00fdt s\u00e1o trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110TQG.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Emery mu\u1ed1n gi\u00fap Ozil h\u1ed3i sinh</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eebng ch\u00e2n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 ngay sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Sau gi\u1ea3i, Ozil c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 nh\u1eadn nhi\u1ec1u l\u1eddi ph\u00ea b\u00ecnh nh\u1ea5t. Ch\u00ednh qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd \u0111\u1ed9i, Oliver Bierhoff \u0111\u00e3 cho bi\u1ebft tr\u00ean b\u00e1o r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c g\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thu\u1ed9c bi\u00ean ch\u1ebf Arsenal l\u00ean tuy\u1ec3n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t sai l\u1ea7m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Emery\" title=\"Emery\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/24/tu-neymar-den-lichtsteiner-emery-dang-hoc-cach-chap-nhan.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ozil v\u00e0 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 anh</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u0111\u00e1nh th\u1ee9c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Ozil \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c giao cho HLV Unai Emery t\u1ea1i Arsenal. V\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia 46 tu\u1ed5i tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng gi\u00fap ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 gi\u00e0u s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o n\u00e0y tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t. \u201cT\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7\u201d, HLV Emery ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ozil. \u201c\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, Ozil l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n gi\u00fap s\u1ee9c cho c\u1eadu \u1ea5y.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n. L\u00fac n\u00e0y Ozil \u0111ang \u0111i ngh\u1ec9 v\u00e0 t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n t\u1ed1t. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u00e2m l\u00fd th\u1eadt t\u1ed1t. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c v\u1edbi Ozil theo ph\u01b0\u01a1ng ph\u00e1p m\u1edbi nh\u1eb1m gi\u00fap c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u00e1t huy t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i hay h\u01a1n.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cM\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 cho Ozil. V\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n mang l\u1ea1i cho h\u1ecd s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin, gi\u00fap h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 h\u01a1n m\u1ed7i ng\u00e0y.\u201d<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 HLV Emery tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-emery-hua-hen-arsenal-se-co-them-bom-tan-172-191120.html\">HLV Emery h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n Arsenal s\u1ebd c\u00f3 th\u00eam \u201cbom t\u1ea5n\u201d</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/emery-len-ke-hoach-tuoc-bang-doi-truong-arsenal-172-191092.html\">Emery l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u01b0\u1edbc b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-hlv-emery-bao-tin-buon-cho-arsenal-172-191065.html\">T\u00e2n HLV Emery b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho Arsenal</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/thuc-hu-vu-arsenal-chi-35-trieu-euro-mua-andre-gomes-172-190877.html\">Th\u1ef1c h\u01b0 v\u1ee5 Arsenal chi 35 tri\u1ec7u euro mua Andre Gomes?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/hlv-emery-muon-arsenal-rut-ruot-real-madrid-172-189735.html\">HLV Emery mu\u1ed1n Arsenal r\u00fat ru\u1ed9t Real Madrid</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4214","checkdouble":"191156"},{"date":"15:15 14/07","title":"HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n Chelsea trao \u0111\u1ed5i \"bom t\u1ea5n\" v\u1edbi Juventus","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/3/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-trao-doi-bom-tan-voi-juventus.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Alvaro Morata l\u1ea5y Gonzalo Higuain, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a Maurizio Sarri, ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m thay Conte d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea9y Morata r\u1eddi Chelsea</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Morata \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Chelsea. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1992 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n, kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng v\u1eady anh c\u00f2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. V\u1edbi phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i t\u1ecf ra kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Morata l\u1ea5y Higuain h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Morata l\u1ea5y Higuain h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/22/Chuyen-nhuong-Chelsea-2018-muon-doi-Morata-lay-Higuain-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea9y Morata kh\u1ecfi Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMorata ch\u1ec9 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 11 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf Premier League m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i, ch\u00ednh m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a anh l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Chelsea x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 5 \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, qua \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/chinh-thuc-chelsea-sa-thai-hlv-antonio-conte-465-191114.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i Conte</span>, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec1n 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n v\u1edbi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 48 tu\u1ed5i. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i Maurizio Sarri \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u thay th\u1ebf Conte, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf London v\u00e0 ch\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nDaily Mail kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh HLV Sarri \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi danh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ea7n mua v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u1ebd b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111i \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, trong s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 c\u1ef1u HLV Napoli mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea9y kh\u1ecfi Stamford Bridge c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Alvaro Morata.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u00d4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Morata, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea9y \u0111i ng\u00f4i sao 26 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u01a1n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Sarri mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Morata l\u1ea5y Higuain</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Chelsea 2018 mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Alvaro Morata l\u1ea5y Gonzalo Higuain, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a Maurizio Sarri, ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1eafp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m thay Conte d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Juventus muon doi Higuain lay Morata\" title=\"Juventus mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Higuain l\u1ea5y Morata\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/3/hlv-sarri-muon-chelsea-trao-doi-bom-tan-voi-juventus.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i Morata l\u1ea5y Higuain</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ee5 th\u1ec3, v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Higuain, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi \u00f4ng \u1edf Napoli. \u00d4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n Chelsea l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i v\u1ec1 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ef1u HLV Napoli h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, Chelsea ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed5i Morata l\u1ea5y c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1987. Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u m\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9 Morata \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Juventus theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n t\u1eeb Real v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin c\u0169ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 26 tu\u1ed5i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Serie A.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c Higuain \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc sang tu\u1ed5i 31 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng duy tr\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Juventus c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn trao \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4213","checkdouble":"191164"},{"date":"15:48 14/07","title":"\"Gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft\" xong Conte, Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n li\u1ec1n 3 t\u00e2n binh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/che.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, The Blues \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn h\u1ecd b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m t\u00e2n HLV Sarri, v\u00e0 Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n 3 t\u00e2n binh trong th\u1eddi gian s\u1edbm nh\u1ea5t.\r\n</h2><h2>Chelsea b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00fac m\u1eafc k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a h\u00e8 t\u1edbi gi\u1edd, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c sa th\u1ea3i Antonio Conte. C\u00f9ng v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u1ec3 thay th\u1ebf, \u0111\u00e1nh d\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t k\u1ef7 nguy\u00ean m\u1edbi. Nh\u1eefng th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 b\u1ecb \u0111\u00ecnh tr\u1ec7 s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, v\u00e0 d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e2m m\u1ed9 The Blues chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n tin vui t\u1edbi t\u1ea5p.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd ch\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3n ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho t\u1eeb Napoli, c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169 c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri. M\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch CLB Italia \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, khi th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e3 &ldquo;s\u1ed1ng l\u1ed7i&rdquo; v\u1edbi Man City v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb nhi\u1ec1u ti\u00ean h\u01a1n c\u1ee7a Chelsea. D\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 Champions League m\u00f9a t\u1edbi, nh\u01b0ng Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111em v\u1ec1 Jorginho, m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 57 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ti\u1ebfp theo, ngay sau khi World Cup 2018 kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00f4 London s\u1ebd l\u00e0m r\u00f5 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 - Thibaut Coutois v\u00e0 Eden Hazard. Song song v\u1edbi \u0111\u00f3, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111em v\u1ec1 2 t\u00e2n binh c\u0169ng c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga, thay th\u1ebf ch\u00ednh 2 tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n 3 t\u00e2n binh ngay khi b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri\" title=\"Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n 3 t\u00e2n binh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/che.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n 3 t\u00e2n binh ngay khi b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m Sarri</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a Courtois v\u1edbi The Blues ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n th\u1eddi h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m, v\u00e0 Chelsea kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u00eam d\u00e0i l\u1eafm m\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9. H\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111em s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 60 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1edbi AS Roma \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecfi mua Alisson Becker, th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Brazil. Hi\u1ec7n nay, Chelsea l\u00e0 CLB m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh m\u1ed9t ng\u1ef1a v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y, sau khi Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat lui \u0111\u1ec3 chuy\u1ec3n h\u01b0\u1edbng sang&hellip; Courtois.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 tr\u1ebb Golovin s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Chelsea. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh, h\u1ecd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chia tay m\u1ed9t trong hai tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t l\u00e0 Eden Hazard ho\u1eb7c Willian, v\u00e0 Golovin s\u1ebd l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean thay th\u1ebf x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng sau s\u1ef1 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T qu\u1ed1c gia.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u00f3n 3 t\u00e2n binh, m\u00f9a h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh \u0111ang s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n bao gi\u1edd h\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-chelsea-chinh-thuc-bo-nhiem-nguoi-thay-the-conte-172-191167.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/cuc-nong-chelsea-chinh-thuc-bo-nhiem-nguoi-thay-the-conte.PNG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-chelsea-chinh-thuc-bo-nhiem-nguoi-thay-the-conte-172-191167.html\">C\u1ef0C N\u00d3NG: Chelsea CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Conte</span><br>\r\nMaurizio Sarri d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea thay Conte \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c The Blues x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn, trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y cho bi\u1ebft \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/chinh-thuc-chelsea-sa-thai-hlv-antonio-conte-465-191114.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/chinh-thuc-chelsea-sa-thai-hlv-antonio-conte.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/chinh-thuc-chelsea-sa-thai-hlv-antonio-conte-465-191114.html\">CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C: Chelsea sa th\u1ea3i HLV Antonio Conte</span><br>\r\nChelsea \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c sa th\u1ea3i HLV Antonio Conte \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ebft th\u00fac nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 d\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cho m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia kh\u00e1c t\u1edbi Stamford Bridge trong giai...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-4-nguoi-that-bai-neu-hlv-sarri-dan-dat-chelsea-thay-conte-172-191110.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/13/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-4-nguoi-that-bai-neu-hlv-sarri-dan-dat-chelsea-thay-conte.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-4-nguoi-that-bai-neu-hlv-sarri-dan-dat-chelsea-thay-conte-172-191110.html\">3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i n\u1ebfu HLV Sarri d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea thay Conte</span><br>\r\nHLV Maurizio Sarri t\u1edbi Chelsea thay Conte ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 th\u1eddi gian, d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i khi \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n s\u00e2n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4212","checkdouble":"191166"},{"date":"15:23 14/07","title":"C\u1ef0C N\u00d3NG: Chelsea CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Conte","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/14/cuc-nong-chelsea-chinh-thuc-bo-nhiem-nguoi-thay-the-conte.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Maurizio Sarri d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea thay Conte \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c The Blues x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn, trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y cho bi\u1ebft \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m HLV Sarri</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nH\u00f4m qua, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/chinh-thuc-chelsea-sa-thai-hlv-antonio-conte-465-191114.html\" target=\"_blank\">Chelsea quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i HLV Conte</span>, th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd b\u1edfi \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o t\u1eeb tr\u01b0\u1edbc. Vi\u1ec7c m\u00e2u thu\u1eabn v\u1edbi c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00e1n \u0111\u00edch \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9&nbsp; 5 t\u1ea1i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh m\u00f9a v\u1eeba r\u1ed3i l\u00e0 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia m\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7c.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Maurizio Sarri d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea thay Conte h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"CH\u00cdNH TH\u1ee8C Maurizio Sarri d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea thay Conte h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/cuc-nong-chelsea-chinh-thuc-bo-nhiem-nguoi-thay-the-conte.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1edbi Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nChelsea ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec1n b\u00f9 9 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng ti\u1ec1n ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng s\u1edbm v\u1edbi Conte, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf. Ch\u1ec9 sau m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn sa th\u1ea3i Conte \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMaurizio Sarri d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea thay Conte \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c The Blues x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn, trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y cho bi\u1ebft \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 58 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 3 n\u0103m v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede Stamford Bridge nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 58 tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn l\u01b0\u01a1ng 5.5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/m\u00f9a. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 Chelsea \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 chi 5 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Sarri v\u1edbi Napoli.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Sarri n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed5 nhi\u1ec7m d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea?</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea, HLV Sarri kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: &ldquo;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ebfn Chelsea v\u00e0 Premier League. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t giai \u0111o\u1ea1n m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea7y th\u00fa v\u1ecb trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. Chelsea l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf Anh v\u00e0 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, t\u00f4i h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi h\u1ecd&rdquo;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Sarri\" title=\"HLV Sarri\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/14/sarri-2.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Sarri h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Chelsea</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;T\u00f4i mong mu\u1ed1n b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c v\u00e0 g\u1eb7p g\u1ee1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 Hai tu\u1ea7n t\u1edbi, sau \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf H\u00e8 2018. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u00e0m quen nhanh nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi, t\u00f4i c\u0169ng hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Chelsea gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Marina Granovskaia n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 HLV sarri: &ldquo;M\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Napoli \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf Serie A. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y HLV Sarri ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p v\u1edbi Chelsea v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb, th\u1eadt may m\u1eafn l\u00e0 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn l\u1eddi&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;\u00d4ng \u1ea5y c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u1edf Serie A v\u00e0 Champions League v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i bi\u1ebft \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Chelsea gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u l\u1edbn, hy v\u1ecdng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 h\u1ee3p t\u00e1c t\u1ed1t&rdquo;.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nR\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 sau khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ra m\u1eaft HLV Sarri \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London s\u1ebd tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0ng t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho. Ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf London v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ra m\u1eaft The Blues, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 chi 53 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4211","checkdouble":"191167"},{"date":"15:59 14/07","title":"Chelsea ch\u1ed1t gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n Eden Hazard cho Real","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/5/31/real-madrid-chot-gia-ban-eden-hazard-cho-real.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea b\u00e1n Eden Hazard cho Real Madrid n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Mirror \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Real chi 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Hazard</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef Ronaldo \u1edf l\u1ea1i, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ed3 \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u1eed th\u00e1ch m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p. Ronaldo k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng 4 n\u0103m v\u1edbi Juventus, anh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u01b0\u01a1ng 30 tri\u1ec7u euro/m\u00f9a \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Turin.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea b\u00e1n Eden Hazard cho Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea b\u00e1n Eden Hazard cho Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/31/real-madrid-chot-gia-ban-eden-hazard-cho-real.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real chi 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua Eden Hazard\u00a0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Real Madrid l\u00e0 t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf Ronaldo, Mbappe v\u00e0 Neymar l\u00e0 2 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u, song PSG h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 c\u1ef1c cao cho b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. H\u1ecd \u0111\u00f2i 400 tri\u1ec7u euro cho Neymar v\u00e0 290 tri\u1ec7u euro cho Mbappe.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng chi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u1ed5ng l\u1ed3 cho hai c\u00e1i t\u00ean k\u1ec3 tr\u00ean, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd nh\u1eafm m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 r\u1ebb h\u01a1n. H\u00f4m qua, Daily Mail kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-san-sang-chi-150-trieu-bang-de-mua-hazard-180-191070.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n mua Hazard c\u1ee7a Chelsea</span>, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 150 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Real chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 nh\u1ecf, \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Los Blancos.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Hazard cho Real v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea b\u00e1n Eden Hazard cho Real Madrid n\u1ebfu \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1edd Mirror \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Eden Hazard Chelsea\" title=\"Eden Hazard Chelsea\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/31/hazard-nen-tu-choi-real-de-tro-thanh-huyen-thoai-cua-chelsea.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea ch\u1ec9 b\u00e1n Eden Hazard v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Sarri m\u1edbi ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n Chelsea thay Conte, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y \u01b0u ti\u00ean gi\u1eef c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i \u1edf l\u1ea1i. Chelsea c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 400.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ec3\u00a0thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p Hazard t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng m\u1edbi, Chelsea ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi Real Madrid. Tuy nhi\u00ean, h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 200 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn v\u00e0 Real s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i suy ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 Hazard ra \u0111i Chelsea s\u1ebd nh\u1eafm Anthony Martial c\u1ee7a MU thay th\u1ebf, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Old Trafford v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi t\u1edbi 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4210","checkdouble":"191169"},{"date":"09:17 14/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng 14/7: Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Colombia t\u1ed1 Barca \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed t\u1ec7 b\u1ea1c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/4/diem-tin-sang-147-nguoi-hung-colombia-to-barca-doi-xu-te-bac.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Colombia t\u1ed1 Barca \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed t\u1ec7 b\u1ea1c, Juve \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Ronaldo, Liverpool s\u1eafp mua th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c c\u00f3 trong \u0111i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng 14/7.</h2><h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Colombia t\u1ed1 Barca \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed t\u1ec7 b\u1ea1c<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Yerry Mina \u2013 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf World Cup 2018 m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng t\u1ed1 c\u00e1o b\u1ecb Barca \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed t\u1ec7 b\u1ea1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"T\u00f4i nh\u1eadn ra m\u00ecnh th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n\u00a0kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ean\u00a0trong danh s\u00e1ch d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. T\u00f4i bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i t\u1ef1 t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh \u1edf nh\u00e0,\" Mina chia s\u1ebb.\u00a0\"Th\u1eadt\u00a0bu\u1ed3n\u00a0khi ph\u1ea3i\u00a0ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn c\u00e1c\u00a0\u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i thi \u0111\u1ea5u qua TV! Ch\u1eb3ng ai mu\u1ed1n\u00a0tr\u1ea3i qua\u00a0c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf\u00a0n\u00e0y\". <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Everton \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Mina v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o\u00a0trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Colombia\u00a0s\u1ebd c\u00f3 su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng 147 Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Colombia t\u1ed1 Barca \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed t\u1ec7 b\u1ea1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin s\u00e1ng 147 Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Colombia t\u1ed1 Barca \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed t\u1ec7 b\u1ea1c h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Diem-tin-sang-147-Nguoi-hung-Colombia-to-Barca-doi-xu-te-bac-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <div class=\"imagecontainer\" style=\"width: 779px;\">\r\n            <table style=\"text-align: center; width: 777px;\">\r\n                <tbody>\r\n                    <tr>\r\n                        <td><em>Mina cho r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed kh\u00f4ng c\u00f4ng b\u1eb1ng t\u1ea1i Barcelona<br>\r\n                        </em></td>\r\n                    </tr>\r\n                </tbody>\r\n            </table>\r\n            </div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Alisson<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo nh\u00e0 b\u00e1o Gianluca Di Mazio c\u1ee7a Sky Sport, Roma \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd h\u1ea1 gi\u00e1 Alisson xu\u1ed1ng c\u00f2n 70 tri\u1ec7u Euro v\u00e0 Liverpool \u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc vi\u1ec7c tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec1n s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Brazil t\u1eeb l\u00e2u \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 Real Madrid v\u00e0 Liverpool. Tuy nhi\u00ean, m\u1ee9c gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao m\u00e0 Roma \u0111\u01b0a ra \u0111\u00e3 bu\u1ed9c L\u1eef \u0111o\u00e0n \u0110\u1ecf ph\u1ea3i r\u00fat lui. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n h\u1ee9ng th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y khi quay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn Thibaut Courtois c\u1ee7a Chelsea.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Chelsea chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ra m\u1eaft HLV m\u1edbi<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 sa th\u1ea3i HLV Conte, CLB Chelsea \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho ra m\u1eaft HLV ti\u1ebfp theo c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng. T\u1edd Sky Sports Italy \u0111\u01b0a tin HLV Maurizio Sarri \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf London \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Brigde. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo c\u00e1c ngu\u1ed3n tin, Sarri s\u1ebd k\u00fd v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng d\u1eabn d\u1eaft Chelsea trong 2 n\u0103m k\u00e8m \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n gia h\u1ea1n 1 n\u0103m. M\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng Sarri nh\u1eadn \u1edf Chelsea l\u00e0 5,3 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng/m\u00f9a. \u0110\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi, huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i t\u1eebng kho\u00e1c \u00e1o CLB, Gianfranco Zola c\u0169ng s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng Sarri tr\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ea1o.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Juve \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft Ronaldo<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng Italia, CLB Juventus d\u1ef1 ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd cho ra m\u1eaft Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 16/7 t\u1edbi sau khi ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha t\u1eeb Real Madrid v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 112 tri\u1ec7u euro. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 b\u1ea3n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 thua th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Neymar sang PSG n\u1ebfu t\u00ednh t\u1ed5ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Real ch\u01b0a c\u1ea7n mua Neymar<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia TBN m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. \u201cV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin cho r\u1eb1ng CLV li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Neymar c\u1ee7a PSG, Real Madrid mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m r\u00f5 r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch \u0111\u01b0a ra b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb n\u00e0o cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. PSG v\u00e0 Real c\u00f3 m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 m\u1eadt thi\u1ebft. N\u1ebfu Real quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o PSG, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ea7n l\u00e0m l\u00e0 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi CLB ch\u1ee7 qu\u1ea3n\u201d, K\u1ec1n k\u1ec1n tr\u1eafng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>M.U mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Maguire<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo\u00a0Daily Mail,\u00a0CLB Man United \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Harry Maguire, ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng gi\u00fap Anh h\u1ea1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ec3 v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ebfn B\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup. Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf\u00a0\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng chi 50 tri\u1ec7u B\u1ea3ng, \u0111\u1ec3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c c\u00e1c \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Th\u00e1i c\u1ee7a Leicester City nh\u1ea3 Maguire.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>HLV Conte c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc ki\u1ec7n Chelsea v\u00ec \"b\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n\" b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo tin t\u1eeb Sky Sport, HLV\u00a0Antonio Conte\u00a0\u0111ang c\u00e2n nh\u1eafc\u00a0ki\u1ec7n\u00a0CLB Chelsea\u00a0l\u00ean t\u00f2a \u00e1n c\u1ee7a FIFA n\u1ebfu CLB n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ecbu thanh to\u00e1n ph\u00ed b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a\u00a0The Blues\u00a0v\u1eeba\u00a0c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh sa th\u1ea3i\u00a0v\u1ecb chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi Italia.\u00a0Nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n n\u00e0y v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ebfn n\u0103m 2019 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge. Tuy nhi\u00ean,\u00a0Chelsea s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng tr\u1ea3 ti\u1ec1n\u00a0b\u1ed3i th\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng.\u00a0<br>\r\n<br>\r\nXem th\u00eam:\u00a0<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-ngay-137-mu-co-nguy-co-lon-de-mat-pogba-184-191118.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 13/7: M.U c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 l\u1edbn \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t Pogba</span><br>\r\n<br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:13.5pt;font-family:Roboto;color:#081F2C\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"4209","checkdouble":"191153"}]}